{"tid":760591,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖］比個大波老闆食左~好爽","createTime":"2018-07-29T16:00:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T00:13:32.000Z","uid":65312,"like":11,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3ecb4de67c61cdc68f22ac65013c292ae7f5a0fc","tid":760591,"uid":65312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T16:00:59.000Z","msg":"豪哥一進公司直接把我的背心撕開，我的身材完整的呈現在他眼前，巨大的胸，些許的體毛。豪哥用舌頭繞著我的乳頭打轉，我從沒被這麼玩過，被這麼刺激像是電流流通全身一樣，渾身沒力靠著桌子邊緣，顫抖著&hellip;還發出了點呻吟聲<br />\n<br />\n「舔一下而已就這麼敏感？」<br />\n<br />\n豪哥發現我這樣的反應後開始加重了玩的力度，不時還變換玩法，捏著咬著我的乳頭，我受不了這樣的玩弄，開始發出聲音<br />\n<br />\n「啊&hellip;豪&hellip;豪哥&hellip;&hellip;停下來啦！啊啊&hellip;&hellip;不要&hellip;&hellip;那裏&hellip;我很敏感！不要捏啦不要捏！！啊啊啊！！」<br />\n<br />\n店裡悶熱讓我的身上流滿了汗，我的胸被豪哥舔的滿奶子口水，褲子內的前列腺液流個不停讓我下半身很不舒服，開始求饒，但豪哥不但沒有停還伸進我的褲檔裡吸住我的肉棒<br />\n<br />\n「你棒子都流水成這樣，原來是個騷貨啊，哈！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/000036_0f200cbfad75ff1a74d455bf48f4a49a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F000036_0f200cbfad75ff1a74d455bf48f4a49a.gif&h=38fb77b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75bbeb6fb69b33c77d063399f74b64f673d8f6d2","tid":760591,"uid":79159,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T16:30:17.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b939d82ac92df1735c43e26823aa2409af55bf","tid":760591,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T16:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2611e9e3853f73479117938dcebd36541b3a9f8","tid":760591,"uid":65312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75bbeb6fb69b33c77d063399f74b64f673d8f6d2","tid":760591,"uid":79159,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy